{"tid":764811,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"少女時代可能於今年下半年推出繼 TTS 之後的第二個子團！","createTime":"2018-08-02T09:12:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T13:16:26.000Z","uid":188406,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6e3078d85e8121a53c162f74e1e65db15b97e578","tid":764811,"uid":188406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:12:27.000Z","msg":"今日 (2日)，根據韓國媒體報導少女時代將於今年下半年推出繼 TTS 之後的第二個子團！<br />\n<br />\n少女時代所屬經紀公司 S.M. Entertainment 也表示：「少女時代正在準備新的子團，子團成員及專輯概念等詳細內容確定後會再另行公布。」<br />\n<br />\n少女時代的第一個子團 TTS 是在2012年4月推出，由成員太妍、Tiffany、徐玄組成，目前 Tiffany 和徐玄已經離開 S.M. Entertainment，TTS 未來活動和少女時代完全體合體計畫皆屬未知，因此新子團消息一出讓粉絲都十分驚喜與期待。<br />\n<br />\nKpopn 的 Annie 報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kpopn.com/2018/08/02/%e5%b0%91%e5%a5%b3%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e5%8f%af%e8%83%bd%e6%96%bc%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%8e%a8%e5%87%ba%e7%b9%bc-tts-%e4%b9%8b%e5%be%8c%e7%9a%84%e7%ac%ac%e4%ba%8c%e5%80%8b%e5%ad%90%e5%9c%98%ef%bc%81/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kpopn.com%2F2018%2F08%2F02%2F%25e5%25b0%2591%25e5%25a5%25b3%25e6%2599%2582%25e4%25bb%25a3%25e5%258f%25af%25e8%2583%25bd%25e6%2596%25bc%25e4%25bb%258a%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e4%25b8%258b%25e5%258d%258a%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e6%258e%25a8%25e5%2587%25ba%25e7%25b9%25bc-tts-%25e4%25b9%258b%25e5%25be%258c%25e7%259a%2584%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25ba%258c%25e5%2580%258b%25e5%25ad%2590%25e5%259c%2598%25ef%25bc%2581%2F&d=x5BhJw%2Fjm72IKdSWcJudscmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7ef8dc34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kpopn.com/2018/08/02/%e5%b0%91%e5%a5%b3%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e5%8f%af%e8%83%bd%e6%96%bc%e4%bb%8a%e5%b9%b4%e4%b8%8b%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%8e%a8%e5%87%ba%e7%b9%bc-tts-%e4%b9%8b%e5%be%8c%e7%9a%84%e7%ac%ac%e4%ba%8c%e5%80%8b%e5%ad%90%e5%9c%98%ef%bc%81/</a>"},{"pid":"48db748e3f9345aee62af2f6a746f1da98d54122","tid":764811,"uid":132587,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T09:16:57.000Z","msg":"個子團就係得泰妍一個 團體式solo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/b